data.description: Welcome home to this elegant, open, and highly functional LIKE NEW home in the desired Willow River Bluffs neighborhood. With all amenities on the main level, this beautiful home offers convenient living and is ready for entertaining. The entire home boasts an abundance of natural light with 9ft ceilings that allow for extra height in the windows! You will truly appreciate the meticulous attention-to-detail with the well-thought-out upgrades and improvements including a 12x20 spacious deck, engineered wood flooring throughout the main level and recently finished lower level as of July 2023. Don?t wait, reach out to schedule your showing today!
